s: A number of potential outcomes for AMS in care homes, some of which had not been reported in previous studies, were identified. The refined list of 14 outcomes will be used in a future study to agree a COS for care home AMS trials."
}
@article{OKELLY2020509,
title = "Rapid diagnosis of seasonal influenza virus and cohorting of hospitalized patients on an influenza ward: a prospective analysis of outcomes",
