To evaluate the in-vitro antibacterial efficacy and kinetic properties of a novel iodine-based compound, iodine lithium alpha-dextrin (ILαD), against Staphylococcus aureus, and compare the in-vitro cytotoxicity profiles of ILαD and PVP-I.
